    <PrimAttribute name="amActive" id="b4028510-d04a-444a-9ee8-00d4f211ac98">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <access>protected</access>
        <text>

This is used to make teh 2 modal voyage allocation forms disappear and re appear if teh planning screen loses focus.

The problem is that making a form visible makes it active which means that the deactive event on the planning screen fires.
In the planning screen deactive event we want to hide the CC forms so we get a loop.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
